  "text": "The solubility data of DCBNT were measured by the dynamic method and collected by the CrystalSCAN system (E1320, HEL Ltd, UK; figure 4 ). The mass of DCBNT was weighed using an analytical balance (CP225D, Sartorius, Germany) with an accuracy of 10 −4 g. Circulating oil solution from a thermostat (Huber CC1-505wl vpc55, Germany) used with an uncertainty of u(T ) = 0.01 K controlled the temperature of the mixture. [CITATION_1] H and 13 C spectra were recorded on a 400 MHz (Bruker AVANCE 400) or 600 MHz (Bruker AVANCE 600) nuclear magnetic resonance spectrometer. 2200  2100  2000  1900  1800  1700  1600  1500  1400  1300  1200  1100  1000  900  800  700  600  500  400  300  200  100  0  - ",
